comments: Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Bates-Diop's (SAS) path and slightly extends his arms as he absorbs the contact on the screen.
Bates-Diop (SAS) briefly grasps Durant's (BKN) arm and marginal contact occurs as he absorbs the contact created by Durant on his post up.
Primo (SAS) reaches in and makes contact with Durant's (BKN) arm, which dislodges the ball on his spin move.
Murray (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Durant (BKN) off ball and cleanly deflects the pass away.
Claxton (BKN) and Murray (SAS) come together and incidental contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball on the perimeter.
Claxton (BKN) reestablishes himself inbounds prior to gaining possession of the loose ball.

Primo (SAS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the offensive loses control of the ball and then is actively guarding an opponent within 3 seconds of them regaining control of the loose ball.
Harden (BKN) reaches for the loose ball and marginal contact occurs with Poeltl's (SAS) shoulder, which does not affect his ability to secure the rebound.
Bembry (BKN) reaches in and makes contact to Walker IV's (SAS) arm, which affects his ability to gather the ball at the end of his drive.
Bates-Diop (SAS) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Claxton (BKN) is slightly late to establish himself in Bates-Diop's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs on the pick.
Poeltl (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Harden (BKN).
Harden (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball on his tie up attempt, but the contact is brief before Bates-Diop (SAS) disengages and a jump ball is not warranted.
Bates-Diop (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Durant (BKN) during the drive.
Bates-Diop (SAS) and Walker IV (SAS) legally contest Durant's (BKN) jump shot attempt as they both avoid contact with his arm or head.
During the rebound, Claxton (BKN) engages with Poeltl (SAS) and marginal contact occurs as the ball takes an awkward bounce off of the rim.
Murray (SAS) engages with Claxton (BKN) and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect Claxton's ability to secure the rebound.
Poeltl (SAS) never establishes himself in Mills' (BKN) path and delivers contact the dislodges him during the screen.
Bates-Diop (SAS) legally contests Durant's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
During the inbound, Bembry (BKN) and Bates-Diop (SAS) engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect Bates-Diop's ability to get to the pass.
Thomas (BKN) can't secure the rebound and is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Bembry (BKN) rests a hand on Bates-Diop's (SAS) front and marginal contact occurs during his last-second shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) cleanly deflects Walker IV's (SAS) pass out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to and maintained by the Spurs.
Poeltl (SAS) rests his hand on Bembry's (BKN) back and marginal contact occurs as they engage during the rebound.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Bates-Diop's (SAS) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Poeltl (SAS) slips the pick and incidental contact occurs as he comes together with Durant (BKN) during his roll to the basket.
Claxton (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Walker IV (SAS).
Harden (BKN) makes clean ball contact on his dislodge attempt during Walker IV's (SAS) driving shot attempt.
During the pick, Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Murray's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Poeltl (SAS) makes clean ball contact on his steal attempts after Harden (BKN) gathers the ball.
Primo (SAS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Murray (SAS) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Harden (BKN).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Harden (BKN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and possession is correctly awarded to the Spurs.
Poeltl (SAS) leans into Bembry (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as they briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Claxton (BKN) moves into and makes contact with Murray's (SAS) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Bembry (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Bates-Diop's (SAS) path and absorbs the contact as the defenders switch on the pick.
Primo (SAS) briefly places a hand on Durant's (BKN) front and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect Durant's SQBR at the start of his drive.
Primo (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Durant (BKN) during his pass at the end of the drive.
There is no clear and conclusive camera angle to determine if Walker IV (SAS) brings two hands to the ball during his dribble, before he gathers and passes.
Mills (BKN) moves laterally into Murray (SAS) and makes contact with his body, which affects his play at the basket.
During the rebound, Primo (SAS) and Harden (BKN) both make clean ball contact to tie it up and a jump ball is correctly called.
Harden (BKN) brings the ball across half-court within 8 seconds of the Nets gaining possession of the jump ball.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Bates-Diop's (SAS) path and absorbs the contact on the screen.
Primo (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Thomas (BKN).
The game clock expired prior to the shot by Walker IV (SAS) and clean block by Harden (BKN).
